# escritha-app — Code Standards (React + Vite + Zustand + Tailwind)

## Folder structure

```
src/
├── assets/             # Static images and files bundled with the app
├── components/
│   └── ui/             # Generic UI Kit (Button, Modal, Avatar, etc.)
├── i18n/               # Internationalization
├── lib/
│   ├── api.ts          # Central HTTP wrapper (apiFetch) — all requests go through here
│   └── document-engine/# Document engine (AST, parsers, serializers)
├── modules/            # Feature-based domain modules
│   ├── <domain>/
│   │   ├── components/ # Components specific to this module
│   │   ├── hooks/      # Hooks and Zustand stores for this module
│   │   ├── pages/      # Screen components (composition layer)
│   │   ├── types/      # Interfaces and types for this module
│   │   └── utils/      # Functions, API calls, transformations
│   └── shared/         # Components shared across modules
├── router/             # Route definitions and ProtectedRoute
├── types/              # Global types
└── utils/              # Global utilities
```

### Where to put things
- Component used in only one module → `modules/<domain>/components/`
- Component used across multiple modules → `modules/shared/` or `components/ui/`
- API logic for a module → `modules/<domain>/utils/<domain>Api.ts`
- Zustand store for a module → `modules/<domain>/hooks/use<Domain>Store.ts`
- Types for a module → `modules/<domain>/types/`
- Global types → `src/types/`

---

## Global naming conventions

- **Folders and files**: `kebab-case` (module directories always lowercase)
- **Component files**: `PascalCase` (e.g. `MyComponent.tsx`)
- **Hook files**: `use<Name>.ts` (e.g. `useEditorStore.ts`)
- **Classes and interfaces**: `PascalCase`
- **Functions and variables**: `camelCase`
- Code, comments, and file names: **English**
- Messages shown to end users (toasts, errors): **Portuguese (pt-BR)**

### Known inconsistency — never replicate
Module directories must be **lowercase** (`modules/my-module`).
The `modules/Home` directory (PascalCase) is a historical mistake — do not copy this pattern.

---

## Creating a new module

```
src/modules/<lowercase-kebab-case>/
├── components/
│   └── MyComponent.tsx
├── hooks/
│   └── use<Domain>Store.ts
├── pages/
│   └── <Domain>Page.tsx
├── types/
│   └── index.ts
└── utils/
    └── <domain>Api.ts
```

